txt.en:
'It appears we may take advantage of the weaker defences at the eastern gate at Durbúrz-stazg, [placeholder]. It is time to test their strength.

'Enter Durbúrz-stazg by the eastern gate and engage the Enemy there. Test their mettle, then return to me. We may learn something about the encampment which may aid us.

'Durbúrz-stazg lies to the north, and the gate you seek opens through the eastern bulwark.'
'You have returned! What did you learn, [placeholder]?'
'Return to Durbúrz-stazg and defeat many of the Enemy there. You may learn something of value to us.'
The Elves of the Golden Host seek a way to cripple the Orcs of Durbúrz-stazg.
Defeated a servant of the Enemy ([placeholder]/[placeholder])
Defeat servants of the Enemy at Durbúrz-stazg ([placeholder]/[placeholder])
Durbúrz-stazg lies to the north of Echad Sirion.\n\nAemeldir has asked you to defeat servants of the Enemy at Durbúrz-stazg. You will need to enter the encampment through the eastern gate.
Talk to Aemeldir at Echad Sirion
Echad Sirion lies to the south of Durbúrz-stazg.\n\nYou should return to Aemeldir with news of your success.
